* D turned at the sound of Vlad's voice, looking the male over and deciding 
that he didn't really like him being so close to Fenox.
For some reason he felt protective and strangly possesive of her, but that 
just might be that she was the first bot he knew and a female.
He didn't know it but the wolf DNA which was fused with him was making him 
react this way, and males were possesive about females.
But D didn't know that it was just his beast mode talking, so he went on 
being unresponsive to it.
D growled at Vlad and the dog-thing behind him as Fenox turned away from him 
to face them, walking up so that his head was right beside Fenox's. He moved 
from behind Fenox and glared at Vlad.*
